name: Tam Giac Mach Homestay - A boutique studio of Westlake Hanoi
notes: Clean and quiet homestay with the lakeview of Westlake, Hanoi. Tam Giac Mach Homestay is a perfect place to rest before and after your trip while doing the amazing Hanoi Loop

name: ★Panorama WestLake View | 2BR Private apartment
notes: This is an apartment with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The wonderful is the apartment is located, in the location overlooking the Westlake and has a very cozy, quiet space suitable for guests who want to enjoy the feeling of peace, a wonderful experience when coming to this apartment.

name: City View Deluxe Room - Old Quarter Unique Style
notes: Located at a peaceflul residential area at the French Quarter of Hanoi, the Hanorama Apartment can be reached by local transportation & taxi and just a quick walk from some of the most iconic places in Hanoi.

name: King Apartment - 2Br in the middel of Hanoi Old Quarter
notes: With French architecture being the main inspiration behind the design of the apartment just as it had on Vietnamese culture, the apartment with a lovely balcony view of the street will let you immerse yourself into real life of a citizen without having even to leave the apartment.

name: The Pianist *-* 2BR with Westlake View
notes: My place is brand new. It’s easy to walk to Truc Bach lake. The environment is really clean and make you feel comfortable to stay near Truc Bach lake. My apartments are also near food street named Ngu Xa with famous dish Rolling Pho.

name: Royal Homestay - Studio in central Hanoi

name: Fairy Rose Homestay - fancy 1Br in Hanoi
notes: Two-bedroom apartment with a dining area and a kitchen. Great locate, 6 minutes-walk to the Hoan Kiem Lake, 15 to the Old Quarter, which are the hottest spots for nightlife and tourism!

name: Starling studio in Ba Dinh district
notes: Top floor (8th). Rooftop accessible. Lift's available. Streets view. Safe European style outlets. Washer, dryer, and dishwasher's available inside!
